title: Youtube chef cooks all the food from 'It's Always Sunny' | Amber Miller | Radio 104.5
text: Ok, this is fantastic - a Youtube chef has recreated all of the (bizzare) food/drinks from "It's Always Sunny In Philadelphia" including: rum ham, milk steak, riot juice, fight milk and grilled Charlie.Try at home at your own risk! Hi, I'm Amber Miller! When I'm not geeking out about music or going to concerts (which doesn't leave a whole lotta time), I'm playing with my dogs (adopt, don't shop!), enjoying craft beer, taking a yoga class or exploring the outdoors. I try to remember to floss regularly, too! Social
